issue.title: Create java model objects for Spotify (and maybe Firebase).
issue.body:
Need java objects representing JSON returned by Spotify API endpoints. Also need model objects for Firebase (exact details TBD).

Some Spotify objects can be found [here](https://github.com/kaaes/spotify-web-api-android/tree/master/spotify-api/src/main/java/kaaes/spotify/webapi/android/models).
See list of relevant endpoints in issue #2.

Also need models for playback change metadata. Good reference [here](http://downloadtheandroidsdk.blogspot.com/2015/08/how-to-get-spotify-metadata-from.html).

issue.title: Create network interaction code for Firebase & Spotify.
issue.body:
[Retrofit Website](http://square.github.io/retrofit/)
# Spotify

Need endpoints that are used for:
- [Recommendations](https://developer.spotify.com/web-api/get-recommendations/)
- [Genres](https://developer.spotify.com/web-api/get-recommendations/#available-genre-seeds)
- [Audio Features](https://developer.spotify.com/web-api/object-model/#audio-features-object)
- [Playlist Info](https://developer.spotify.com/web-api/object-model/#playlist-object-full)
# Firebase

Need to:
- Authenticate users [User object]
- Save/modify user neural net data per user (Not MVP) 
- Save/modify user playlists [Firebase Playlist object =? list of spotify track ids]
- Sync playlists with playlist changes for Spotify (Not MVP)

issue.title: Connect EEG headset to android phone.
issue.body:
Update Arduino code to return JSON in convenient format. Also add code to access serial data from the USB port.

May have relevant snippets of code. Will try to attach later.
